{"nodes":[{"pos":[12,49],"content":"Compiler Error C2750 | Microsoft Docs","needQuote":false,"needEscape":true,"nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C2750 | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,37]}]},{"pos":[597,617],"content":"Compiler Error C2750","linkify":"Compiler Error C2750","nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C2750","pos":[0,20]}]},{"content":"'type' : cannot use 'new' on the reference type; use 'gcnew' instead","pos":[618,686]},{"pos":[693,878],"content":"To create an instance of a CLR type, which causes the instance to be placed on the garbage-collected heap, you must use <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>gcnew<ept id=\"p1\">](../../windows/ref-new-gcnew-cpp-component-extensions.md)</ept>.","source":"To create an instance of a CLR type, which causes the instance to be placed on the garbage-collected heap, you must use [gcnew](../../windows/ref-new-gcnew-cpp-component-extensions.md)."},{"content":"The following sample generates C2750:","pos":[885,922]}],"content":"---\ntitle: \"Compiler Error C2750 | Microsoft Docs\"\nms.custom: \"\"\nms.date: \"11/04/2016\"\nms.reviewer: \"\"\nms.suite: \"\"\nms.technology: \n  - \"devlang-cpp\"\nms.tgt_pltfrm: \"\"\nms.topic: \"error-reference\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"C2750\"\ndev_langs: \n  - \"C++\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"C2750\"\nms.assetid: 30450034-feb5-448c-9655-b8c5f3639695\ncaps.latest.revision: 8\nauthor: \"corob-msft\"\nms.author: \"corob\"\nmanager: \"ghogen\"\ntranslation.priority.ht: \n  - \"cs-cz\"\n  - \"de-de\"\n  - \"es-es\"\n  - \"fr-fr\"\n  - \"it-it\"\n  - \"ja-jp\"\n  - \"ko-kr\"\n  - \"pl-pl\"\n  - \"pt-br\"\n  - \"ru-ru\"\n  - \"tr-tr\"\n  - \"zh-cn\"\n  - \"zh-tw\"\n---\n# Compiler Error C2750\n'type' : cannot use 'new' on the reference type; use 'gcnew' instead  \n  \n To create an instance of a CLR type, which causes the instance to be placed on the garbage-collected heap, you must use [gcnew](../../windows/ref-new-gcnew-cpp-component-extensions.md).  \n  \n The following sample generates C2750:  \n  \n```  \n// C2750.cpp  \n// compile with: /clr  \nref struct Y1 {};  \n  \nint main() {  \n   Y1 ^ x = new Y1;   // C2750  \n  \n   // try the following line instead  \n   Y1 ^ x2 = gcnew Y1;  \n}  \n```"}